author: @문예예스
text:
힘들때마다 나에게 가장 먼저 떠오르는 사람은 너였어. 항상 곁을 지켜주고, 행복한 미소로 힘을 줬던 너. 그 순간들이 나에게 얼마나 큰 위로가 되었는지, 그리고 네가 내게 얼마나 소중한 존재인지 항상 마음속에 간직하고 있어.

오늘 너에게 내가 힘들 때마다 들었던 노래를 선물하고 싶어. 이 노래를 들으면, 그때 내가 느꼈던 따스한 위로가 너에게도 전해졌으면 좋겠어. 너도 가끔은 힘들 때가 있겠지만, 그럴 때 이 노래가 네 마음을 어루만져 주길 바라. 언제나처럼 난 네 곁에 있을 거야, 너처럼.

네가 있어 나는 참 다행이고, 그래서 매일매일 고마워. 너는 내가 알기에 가장 소중한 사람 중 한 명이야. 오늘도, 앞으로도 행복한 순간들로 가득 채워지길 바랄게.

생일 진심으로 축하해 승빈아

-예영이가

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is a diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. I sincerely apologize, but the visual effects of EXO are too powerful, as soon as they appear on the stage, they capture you with their dazzle, not letting you go until the very end. It's been a whole 11 years, but they simply have no equal in live performances.

author: @liza_pet
text:
As many professional musicians, soloists, idols say, Kyungsoo songs may seem easy only at first glance, but when you start singing you realize how difficult it is. The pure truth is how well Kyungsoo owns his voice with his vocals

author: @liza_pet
text:
Baby Kyungsoo is the cutest, polite, and humble idol in the entire K-POP industry. Although he does not consider himself cute and does not 
like to be called that, but it's the truth and he 
has absolutely nothing to do to be so cute. 
I love him madly for such spontaneity, sincerity and absolutely unique vocals that you can listen to endlessly.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

거울 앞에 서는 것도 머뭇대
이 표정은 또 왜 이리도 어색해

아름다운 건 늘 소중하고
잠시 머물다 아득히 멀어져도
늘 마주 보듯 평범한
일상을 채울 마음의 눈

그 안에 감춰둔 외로움도
잠시 머물 수 있게 해
그저 바라봐
부드러운 바람이 불면

author: @liza_pet
text:
I just love how Kyungsoo dances absolutely 
every movement of his, and in absolutely any choreography so smooth and gentle that it seems as if he does not make any effort everything happens so naturally, of course, 
he is given such plasticity by nature.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Do Kyungsoo just has an unrealistically beautiful face and is literally getting more beautiful every day. He is exactly the kind of person who suits absolutely any style, hairstyle and concept, as evidenced by numerous EXO albums, numerous advertising and numerous acting shots of Kyungsoo, which are so different in a variety 
of roles and images.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Do Kyungsoo is just an incredible person that I will never stop admiring. At first glance, the album, the songs and his vocals may seem simple, but in fact it is not so at all. A large range does not make you a better vocalist yet, because another important role is played by the "technique", which Kyungsoo undoubtedly has great. He has such control over his voice that he makes all the transitions from low to high notes completely smoothly and even seems to make no effort. Quite naturally, during a song, it can change its timbre from incredibly sweet to sexually rude and sound simply amazing in each. Kyungsoo is one of those few vocalists who can make your heart flutter.
/
This album is something unique that Kyungsoo has put his soul into. He himself wrote the lyrics for the title song "Rose", and also took a direct part in writing each song. He learned to play guitar while still serving in the army, studied independently and played each of his songs from the album to record. He has recorded songs in several languages "Korean, English, Spanish" which not everyone does.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text:
EXO is my very first and only favorite band in the entire K-POP industry and baby Kyungsoo "D.O." is my very first and only bias in the entire K-POP industry. Or rather, it was love at first sight, of course all the members are unrealistically talented beauties, but it was baby D.O. who attracted my attention as soon as I saw him 
for the first time.

author: @prayatna7109
text:
[Verse 1]

I feel like I'm losing myself in the

Many emotions that have gone by

From some point, I became used to

The rules I follow to hide my heart

 

[Verse 2]

How far have I come now

I ran, only looking forward

Now I’m scared to look back

The words I've postponed

 

[Pre-Chorus]

Like time passes, inside of me

Times when I happy, days where

I cried so much my chest went numb

Like the sun that rises and sets every day

And the moon, I send them away naturally

 

[Chorus]

Sometimes I cry (Ay, yo)

Sometimes I laugh (Ay, yo)

I have expectations (Ay, yo)

And I go through pain (Ay, yo) (Ay, yo)

I get butterflies once again (Ay, yo)

And become dull (Ay, yo)

Following my heart, the way that I am

 

[Post-Chorus]

Like the countless stars

I'm always in the same place

I’ll shine on you with all the light I have

So don't hide yourself, will you show me you?

Be comfortable with the way you are

That's right, it's ok to be ok

 

[Verse 3]

Today, for the first time

I face my honest heart

Even looking in the mirror is hard

Why is this facial expression so awkward?

 

[Verse 4]

Beautiful things are always precious

Even if you stay for a while and then leave

Like the ordinary occurrences I see everyday

Somehow I still want to fill up my daily life

 

[Pre-Chorus]

The loneliness that's stayed hidden inside

Let it linger for a little

Just look at it

If the soft breeze blows

Open your heart, the day will pass

[Chorus]

Sometimes I cry (Ay, yo)

Sometimes I laugh (Ay, yo)

I have expectations (Ay, yo)

And I go through pain (Ay, yo) (Ay, yo)

I get butterflies once again (Ay, yo)

And become dull (Ay, yo)

Following my heart, the way that I am

 

[Post-Chorus]

Like the countless stars

I'm always in the same place

I'll shine on you with all the light I have

So don't hide yourself, will you show me you?

Be comfortable with the way you are

That’s right, it’s ok to be ok

 

[Bridge]

The memories that fill both hands

Our precious story

A sincere heart

If you can still remember them after time passes

Will you be able to say

That you were happy too?

 

[Chorus]

I cried with you (Ay, yo)

And we laughed together (Ay, yo)

I had expectations (Ay, yo)

And I went through pain (Ay, yo)

I poured out everything (Ay, yo)

And I loved (Ay, yo)

Following my heart, the way that I am

 

[Post-Chorus]

The troubles you couldn't talk about

The spots with deep scars

The time passing at the same pace

Like always, I’ll wash them away

So it's ok to live like flowing water

It's just ok to be ok.

text: 경수야 나 오늘 너무 힘들었어 편의점 알바가 끝나갈 때쯤 연세 있으신 손님 네다섯분이 오셨는데 나보고 술에 어울리는 안주 추천을 해달래 그래서 내가 안주를 안 먹어봐서 추천을 못 해드릴 것 같다고 했더니 할아버지 한 분께서 그렇게 손님 응대를 하면 안되는거라고 안먹어봤어도 추천을 해야하는거고 아니면 알아서 잘 찾아보세요~ 이렇게 말했어야 하는거래 나는 최대한 내 의사 전달해드리려고 안주 안먹어봤는데 먹어본 척 추천해드리는건 거짓이라서 그런거라고 말씀드렸는데 어린애가 기어오른다고 생각하셨나봐 물건 던지고 엄청 윽박지르고 편의점 밖 의자에서 술 먹으러가셨어 난 내가 잘못한게 없다고 생각했는데 눈물이 나와서 필사적으로 참으려고 했거든 눈물 흘리면 내가 지는 것 같잖아 근데 집에 와서 너무 서럽고 힘들어서 너 노래 들으면서 울고 있어 제일 싫은 건 난 분명 잘못 응대하지 않았다고 생각했는데 집에 와서 다시 생각해보니 내 말투가 잘못됐나 생각하게 된다는거야 지금까지는 알바할때 아무리 힘든 일이 있어도 저 사람이 잘못된거니 괜찮다고 생각했는데 아닌가봐 나 너무 힘들어 힘들어서 죽어버릴 것 같아

author: @kemika-we
text:
My senses are numbing
Because of the thick emotions passing
Now I’m used to
Hiding my heart
How far have I come?
I only ran forward
So I’m afraid to look back
On all the pushed back stories

Like time passing
All the happy days
And all the heart-breaking days
I’m naturally letting them go
Like the sun and moon that rises and sets

Sometimes, I cried, sometimes, I laughed
I was hopeful, I was in pain
My heart fluttered, my heart numbed
I followed my heart, just as it is

Like the countless stars
Always in the same place
I’ll shine as much as I can
So don’t hide yourself but show me
You, just as you are, it’s alright, it’s alright

Today, for the first time
I faced my honest heart
I even hesitate to stand in front of the mirror
Why is my face so awkward?

What’s beautiful is always precious
Even if it stays for a moment and goes far away later
The eyes of my heart fill up the ordinary moments
As if it’s always looking

The loneliness hidden inside
Makes me stay for a bit
I’m just looking
When the gentle breeze blows
I open my heart and another day passes

Sometimes, I cried, sometimes, I laughed
I was hopeful, I was in pain
My heart fluttered, my heart numbed
I followed my heart, just as it is

Like the countless stars
Always in the same place
I’ll shine as much as I can
So don’t hide yourself but show me
You, just as you are, it’s alright, it’s alright

The memories that fill our hands
Is our precious story
My heart is filled with the truth
If you can remember again after time
Will you be able to say
That you were happy too?

I cried with you, I laughed with you
I had high hopes for you, I was pained because of you
I spilled out my all and loved you
However my heart led me

All the unspoken worries
All the deeply paved scars
Time always passes at the same speed
It will wash it all away just like always
So you can just go with the flow, it’s alright, it’s alright

text:
댓글도 안쓰고 그냥 듣고만 가는데 참 볼때마다 느끼는거지만 무덤덤한 표정속에 그동안 연예인을 하며 느꼈을 행복과 힘듦이 다 느껴진다
 연예인이란 직업으로 살면서 쉽지않았을텐데 연차가 쌓이고 살면서 느낀 경험들을 우리에게 그땐 그랬어하며 얘기하고  다른직업을 가진 모든 사회인들에게 응원과 위로를 주는거같다 사회속에 묻힌 나의 진짜 모습을 되돌아보게하는 또는 어릴때의 내가 미래를 상상하며 설레이는 모습들도 생각들게 하고 13살에 엑소를 엄청 좋아하던 내모습과 삶에 치여 점점 잊혀져가 이제 20대중반에 든 지금은 참... 열정적으로 좋아했던때만큼은 아니더라도 멀리서 잔잔히 응원할게요  부디 오래오래 좋은노래 내주세요

author: @liza_pet
text: Kyungsoo just has an unrealistically beautiful face and is literally getting more beautiful every day. He is exactly the kind of person who suits absolutely any style, hairstyle and concept, as evidenced by numerous EXO albums, numerous advertising and numerous acting shots of Kyungsoo, which are so different in a variety of roles and images.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is my very first and only favorite band in the entire K-POP industry and baby Kyungsoo "D.O." is my very first and only bias in the entire K-POP industry. Or rather, it was love at first sight, of course all the members are unrealistically talented beauties, but it was baby D.O. who attracted my attention as soon as I saw him for the first time.

text: I still remember how much I cried the day this dropped.. He just went live and started talking about his military service and answered all our questions and said that he is preparing for his album and is going to film his movies later this year.. Said that as a gift from him he recorded a live ver. of that's okay because we loved it so much.. Giggling the whole live and interacting with sehun then closing his healing 30 mins live and suddenly this video dropped, I went right away to check it out and I sobbed for like the fifth time this day.. It was a dream of mine to have him sing my favorite ever song live and he fulfilled my dream once he got discharged.. That day was really one of the happiest days of my life and i thank kyungsoo for giving us such a memorable day~ღ

author: @nisfiaelfida5165
text:
Sudah lama berlalu 
Inderaku yang mati rasa dalam perasaan 
Sejak kapankah aku terbiasa dengannya
Cara untuk menyembunyikan perasaanku 
 
Dimanakah aku berada
Aku hanya menatap ke depan dan terus berlari 
Mengapa aku begitu takut untuk berbalik
Semua kisah yang ku simpan 
 
Seiring berjalannya waktu, di dalam hatiku 
Saat-saat aku bahagia dulu 
Bahkan hari yang penuh air mata sebanyak hatiku yang mati rasa 
Setiap hari matahari terbit dan terbenam dengan cara yang sama 
Seperti bulan itu yang terbenam dengan sendirinya 
 
Terkadang aku menangis, terkadang aku tertawa 
Tidakkah berharap itu menyakitkan? 
Aku menjadi berdebar kemudian kembali mati rasa 
Seperti itulah hatiku bereaksi, dengan apa adanya
 
Seperti bintang yang tak terhitung jumlahnya 
Itu selalu ada di tempat yang sama 
Aku akan bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri 
Jangan bersembunyi, aku akan menunjukannya padamu dengan pasti
Dirimu yang seperti itu, ya, itu tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa 
 
Hari ini, untuk pertama kalinya 
Aku melihat hatiku yang sebenarnya 
Di depan cermin, aku bahkan berdiri dengan begitu ragu 
Lagi, mengapa raut wajahku ini terlihat begitu canggung?
 
Sesuatu yang indah, itu selalu berharga 
Itu selalu tinggal untuk sesaat dan menjauh dengan perlahan 
Itu selalu jelas seperti yang terlihat 
Mata hati memenuhi kehidupan sehari-hari
 
Bahkan kesepian yang tersembunyi di dalam hatimu 
Itu bisa tetap berada disana untuk sesaat 
Karna itu, cobalah kau lihat
Saat angin yang lembut berhembus 
Bukalah hatimu, itu adalah hari untuk melaluinya 
 
Terkadang aku menangis, terkadang aku tertawa

Kenangan yang memenuhi kedua tanganmu
Kisah kita yang berharga 
Sebuah hati yang penuh ketulusan 
Andai waktu berlalu dan kau bisa mengingatnya kembali 
Bisakah kau memberitahuku?
Bahwa kau juga bahagia 
 
Aku menangis dan tertawa bersamamu 
Tidakkah berharap itu menyakitkan? 
Aku mencurahkan semuanya dan mencintaimu 
Seperti itulah hatiku bereaksi, dengan apa adanya
 
Kekhawatiran yang tak terucapkan 
Itu menjadi luka yang kian dalam 
Waktu selalu berlalu dengan kecepatan yang sama 
Selalu seperti itu, itu akan menghapusnya 
Meski hidup mengalir seperti itu, tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa

author: @kyungsoodo3288
text:
A letter from Kyungsoo


Dear ROSE,

How are you, MY LOVE? DAD told me you're worried and sad (sigh). I know how hard it is to be away from each other but DON'T WORRY my training will be over soon and we'll get to see each other gain. If CRYING OUT loud will somehow make you feel comfortable and ease, feel free to do it, THAT'S OKAY, but do it once (tease). Do you remember when you TELL ME WHAT IS LOVE? You give and define all the meanings of love. Then you make me feel it and realize how love defies everything. When I haven't met you, I don't believe in love. But the moment I laid my eyes on you, I know IT'S LOVE. Anyway, if you'd ask me, I'm doing good, I'M FINE. So please, stop worrying. There will be no more GOODBYE SUMMER, I promise. Just remember, I'M GONNA LOVE YOU FOR LIFE.

D.O.

author: @nurinazatul
text:
Senses that have become dull 
Due to the many feelings that have passed by 
Ways of hiding my true heart 
That I’ve become used to since some time 
Where have I come to? I’ve only ran looking forward 
I’m scared of looking back for some reason 
Stories I’ve pushed back
As time goes by,
I send away the happy times and the tearful days that made my chest hurt naturally like the sun and that moon that rise and fall every day, altogether 
Sometimes we cry, sometimes we laugh We expect things and get hurt 
We flutter in excitement again and become dulled 
Just do what your heart pleases 
Just like how countless stars did, always [in] the same spot you will shine brightly on your own 
Dont hide yourself Will you show me yourself, comfortably? 
Just as yourself 
That’s right, it’s okay to be okay... 

Today, I face my honest feelings for the first time 
I hesitate to stand in front of the mirror Why is my expression this awkward? Beautiful things are always precious, they are the eye of one’s heart 
Even if you’re here for only a bit and then go far away, 
they’ll fill up the plain-as-ever, everyday life 
They even let the loneliness you’ve hid within stay for a brief moment 
Just look: when the soft wind blows, open up your heart, and the day will pass Sometimes we cry, sometimes we laugh We expect things and get hurt 
We flutter in excitement again and become dulled 
Just do what your heart pleases 
Just like how countless stars did, always [in] the same spot 
You will shine brightly on your own
Dont hide yourself 
Will you show me yourself, comfortably? Just as yourself 
That’s right, it’s okay to be okay 
The memories that will fill our two hands are our precious story 
If the heart full of sincerity can remember it after time has passed 
Will you be able to say it? 
That you were happy too?... 

I cried with you and smiled together
We expected things and got hurt 
We poured in our all and loved [each other] 
Just the way the heart desired 
A concern that can’t be brought up 
A place where a deep wound has been made 
Time, always flowing at the same speed, will wash it away like it has done every time 
Even if you live like how [time] flows, it’s okay to be okay... 

for my own reference heheh 🥲

author: @mellv3967
text: Creo que es la primera vez que puedo sentir que colapso, y la verdad en parte es mi culpa por querer hacerme un bien. Siempre supe que ingresar a esta universidad no iba a ser fácil y que es muy exigente, y la verdad es que hasta ahora puedo decir que estoy orgullosa de hacer nivelación aquí, ojalá llegue a pasar a primer semestre. El punto es que, todo esto me está afectando, desde que me metí a un curso para prepararme y pasar nivelación mis horarios se han vuelto super que pesados, no tengo momentos para mi, casi no duermo, pensé que mis notas subirían pero realmente han sido del asco y estoy a punto de perder dos materias, me la paso llorando todo el rato, los momentos que quiero practicar en ejercicios me lo consume otra materia y no puedo, y ver que a otros compañeros le funciona este curso para el pre me hace sentir insuficiente. No sé que hacer, además que me sentiria muy mal por haber hecho gastar a mis padres y que a la final no me haya resultado nada. Escuchar la voz de Kyungsoo me hace sentir más relajada a pesar de que todo lo que he deseado desde pequeña se me está derrumbando por una decisión que yo tomé.

author: @joanyb
text:
수정) 이전에 썼다가 지운 댓글이지만 마음은 남겨두고 싶어서 다시 올려요.

제가 글재주는 영 없는데, 마음을 최대한 잘 표현할 수 있도록 해볼게요.
이 세상에 좋은 곡들은 참 많아요. 근데 단순히 좋은 걸 넘어서 각자의 마음에 퍼즐 조각처럼 딱 들어맞는 곡은 그리 많지 않다고 생각해요. 그렇기 때문에 살면서 그런 곡을 알게 되었다면 정말 큰 축복이고 행운이라고 생각해요. 비록 며칠 전에 알게 된 노래지만, '괜찮아도 괜찮아'가 저한테 그런 존재에요. 숱하게 스쳐간 감정들과 우울에 잠식되고, 속이 뒤틀리고 문드러지고 하는데, 분명 고통스러운데, 참 이상하게도 동시에 멍한 느낌이 들어요. 붕 떠있는 것처럼요. 그게 너무 싫고 괴롭더라구요. 이러지도 저러지도 못하고, 머릿속이 뿌옇고, 벗어나기가 너무 힘들고 전 너무 약해서 금방 무너져버려요. 그럼 그런 제 자신이 너무 한심하고 증오스럽고 그래서 또 저 밑으로 가라앉아요. 제가 이 모양이라, "넌 이겨낼 수 있다", "다 지나고 나면 넌 예쁘게 피어날 거다", "너 자신을 믿어라" 이런 메세지를 전하는 노래들을 듣는 게 오히려 저를 더 괴롭게 했어요. 이거 쓰면서 글로 읽으니 참 못났네요...ㅎㅎ
근데 이 노래는 적어도 제가 받아들이기엔 그런 말을 하는 게 아니라 그냥 아무 말 없이 저를 꽉 안아주는 느낌이었어요. 따뜻한 품에 안기는 기분이었어요. 사실 우리 모두 인간으로서 살면서 비슷한 경험들을 하고, 공감대를 형성하고 뭐 그럴 수는 있어도 어쨌든 타인의 아픔을 날 것 그대로 온전히 이해할 수는 없잖아요. 본인의 아픔은 오로지 본인만이 온전히 느끼는 거니까. 그래서 저는 힘내라는 말, 괜찮을 거라는 말을 안 하는 이 노래 가사가 너무 와닿아요. 우리 존재들 사이의 어쩔 수 없는 거리를 자각하고, 그래서 섣불리 당신이 짊어지고 있는 마음의 무게에 대해 뭐라 할 순 없지만, 우리 모두 존재 자체가 별이고 각자의 몫으로 이 세상을 빛낸다는 말을 해주는 것 같아서 그러니 어떤 모습이든 괜찮아도 괜찮다고 해주는 것 같아서, 진심으로 힘이 돼요.
정말 진심으로 감사드려요. 이렇게 좋은 노래를 만들어주셔서. 제게 너무나도 큰 선물을 주신 디오님, 부디 행복하시기를 바라요. 전역 축하드리고 건강 조심하세요.이제 열혈팬이 된 저는 오늘부터 쭉 응원하겠습니다. 화이팅!

author: @saeajah3588
text:
How to stream : 
Use 1 account on 1 device having 1 IP address
Stay logged in while streaming
Watch 3-4 other MVs in between the MV you're focusing on (at least 10-15 minutes)
(OPTIONAL - Skip if you don't want to) Remove the MV from your Watch History (WAIT AT LEAST 10-15 MINUTES AFTER WATCHING)
Refresh the page a few times before rewatching the MV
Watch the full video and do NOT skip forward
Comment/interact with other comments at least once an hour
Switch to a different account after 8-10 hours of streaming
Do NOT use a playlist in the first 24 hours
Do NOT mute the video, you can mute your device instead
Do NOT loop/replay the video

author: @therollingpin5850
text: This song makes me shed tears every time I listen to it. Being an EXOL saved me from anxiety and overthinking. Most of the time I pity myself because I don't have friends. There are times that I compare myself to others who have many people by their side. But because of EXO, I somehow overcome it. They became my resting place whenever I feel tired. Their video cheers me up whenever I feel down. They became the reason of my smile and why I'm not giving up. They became my strength. Even though I don't have anyone on my side, I believe that EXO is there for me. It may not be physically, but their existence already means a lot for me. I hope we can be friends, EXOLs.... We are one, EXO Saranghaja!

author: @miamoresoo2741
text:
Wrote this poem for you almost a year back. Posting it again, now that I can actually see you while you are singing this soulful song. 
.
.
You came into my life 
During my most troubled times
When darkness became my ally
And my soul sought for some light

As my mind wandered around
Hopelessly lost in despair
You came like a ray of sunshine
Spreading your warmth the way I desired

Your voice became my sweet lullaby
Your laughter became my safe haven
The more I heard and learned about you
The calmer my aching heart became

Now, you give me hope, you give me light
You give me the strength to feel alive
You are my dream, a breath of fresh air
One thing I never knew my life required

이 표정은 또 왜 이리도 어색해

아름다운 건 늘 소중하고

늘 마주 보듯 평범한

잠시 머물 수 있게 해
그저 바라봐

때론 울고 때론 웃고

두 손에 가득 채워질 추억들은
소중한 우리 이야기
진심이 담긴 마음이
시간이 지나 다시 기억할 수 있다면
말할 수 있을까
너도 행복했다고

너와 울고 같이 웃고
기대하고 아파했지
모든 걸 쏟고 사랑하고
마음이 가는 대로 있는 그대로

author: @zonpwintphyu3146
text:
Dear international friends,

Sorry for posting a message here! 🙏

In our country Myanmar, the military has detained our elected democratic government, party leaders and political activists.
This is a breach of democracy in the nation. National television channels, some phone services and internet services are cut out nationwide.Please be aware of what is happening in Myanmar right now and support us. This is against the will of citizens. They are using weapons to shut us out.

We, people from Myanmar need urgent ATTENTION and ACTION from the people, governments around the WORLD.
Myanmar military is repeating the ugliest history of conducting a coup over unfounded, false claims of vote fraudulent...
Myanmar army has coup the Nation and announced to be in power for a year. We need to let the world to know that this is not our choice. 

For International friends, please help us in anyway you can. Let the world know by sharing this message. 🙏

#Myanmarcoup 
#myanmar_military_coup
#save_myanmar
#Myanmar

text:
Dear All the friends outside of Myanmar, 

We are being cut off all the telecommunications and broadcasting, currently only connection is through WIFI and not sure when it will be get cut off as well . This is offending the human right. 

Their act of trying to close eyes and ears is against the people right. 
Such act is unacceptable and please voice out on behalf of us. 
We are stand firm with our leader Daw Aung San Su Kyi and truly believe that she is leading us to the brighter future of democratic country. 

We appreciate your strong support and sincerely thankful. 
Please help us with love and support to over this. 

#save Myanmar

We  urge  your urgent attention as our democratically elected leaders including State Counsellor Aung San Suu Kyi, President Win Myint along with senior government officials, and the  elected members of parliament have now been detained by the military. 我们需要您采取紧急适当的行动和干预，以停止这场军事政变，以保护缅甸人民和民主选举产生的全国民主政府联盟。

life is short and tomorrow is not promised to anyone, anywhere. some people die in their sleep, i am telling this for us to realize that there really is an urgency for change of heart. i don't want anyone else to be in danger of losing their own soul just because no one told them about this. 

please let us all stop involving ourselves in magic, new age, chakras, divinations, spiritualism, witchcraft, law of attraction, astral projection,tarot, etc. these are all demonic. it brings good to you because it wants you to stay until your soul is already tied to it. it's wolves in sheep's clothing! 

if this life we have is temporary, there is eternal life waiting on the other side. same thing, if there is one death on earth then there's eternal death. it's either heaven or hell and it's real, no doubt, just look around and you'll see the difference. if we were to all die tonight where would you be after death? accept Jesus as your Lord and Savior now, that'll be the best decision you've ever made

we don't just live to die, Romans 6:23 "For the wages of sin is death, but the gift of God is eternal life in Christ Jesus our Lord." we die because all of us sinned and that's one enough reason why we need to get right with God. 

REPENT, we all sinned against GOD and after asking for forgiveness, we need to turn away from it. 

ACCEPT JESUS AS YOUR LORD AND SAVIOR, we all will die and all will be judged, JESUS died on the cross as wages for our sins and if we don't accept it, we will die for our own in the eternal lake of fire. 

BE BORN AGAIN, im not talking about religion, its about laying down your past self and making your identity and life new through and for JESUS. 

GOD loves us all and we must get right back with HIM. this world will perish, all people will die, but GOD is eternal and stop the doubt. believe to see! 

God bless you all, brothers and sisters!

author: @rosedyo
text:
I love reading all the long comments praising him.

I have known Kyungsoo since 100dmp and I will continue to brag that fact to the end. After a year since 100dmp, I kept looking for Kyungsoo and Exo by myself, I finally fell in love with them. I wasn’t so interested in kpop before, that’s why I needed a year to search and understand about them. It was like a miracle, he took me to Exo without I realized it. 

Kyungsoo is not like a typical k-idol. My first impression of him was that he didn't do too much make-up, didn't do aegyo, his voice was so deep and his voice I couldn't describe it, it just sounded very good to me. I don’t complain about anyone else but he is just unique which makes me attracted more to him. Once I got to know Exo, despite having different characters, I love them all. Their vocals are incomparable. They continue to improve every year.

Exo is my first and last idol.  Please stay together until the end. Can't wait for Exo comeback! And ofcos D.O. first solo!

author: @idkwhoiam3177
text:
Not an exo-l but I genuinely love and admire this guy. Honestly speaking, I never saw an idol with such personality.  He is always so humble, honest and leads a simple life. The interesting part about him is that he only does things that he wants to do, doesn't give a fc*k about what others want him to do ( he shaved his head for a role, right?) Not everyone has this kind of courage! Not to mention, hes such a well-rounded artist too. His vocal tone is the best one for me in whole kpop. His tone and way of singing gives off western rnb vibe. I would definitely love to hear more songs from him.
P.S: exo-ls really should be proud bcoz they have such an amazing person as their idol.

author: @ItinakdangAsulTV
text:
To be honest, I went in to denial stage before becoming an EXO fan (EXO-L).

It's D.O. who introduced me to the group anyway. I've known him first as an actor but I fell in love with him as a singer. Did I fall for his acting skills? Yes! BUT I fell deeper for his voice and his personality. You read it right, His unique traits pulled me closer to him. Indeed he's totally unique. I can see and feel his sincerity. You can see through his eyes how genuine he is. He's that person who you'd feel safe around. Someone who'll remind you to keep going when you want to give up. He's that kind of person who'll always be behind you to cheer you up when you feel so down. Something like that. I saw that from his personality. He's one of a kind. You'll see the truthfullness in his eyes. I'm just so lucky to have finally have this song of him to listen to. 

So whatever happens, I'll always support this guy 'coz you can never find someone like him again.

수많은 별이 그랬듯이
언제나 같은 자리
제 몫의 빛으로 환하게 비출 테니
숨기지 말고 너를 보여줄래 편히
네 모습 그대로 그래 괜찮아 괜찮아도

오늘 난 처음으로
솔직한 내 마음을 마주해
거울 앞에 서는 것도 머뭇대
이 표정은 또 왜 이리도 어색해

아름다운 건 늘 소중하고
잠시 머물다 아득히 멀어져도
늘 마주 보듯 평범한
일상을 채울 마음의 눈

그 안에 감춰둔 외로움도
잠시 머물 수 있게 해
그저 바라봐
부드러운 바람이 불면
마음을 열어 지나갈 하루야

때론 울고 때론 웃고
기대하고 아파하지
다시 설레고 무뎌지고
마음이 가는 대로 있는 그대로

수많은 별이 그랬듯이
언제나 같은 자리
제 몫의 빛으로 환하게 비출 테니
숨기지 말고 너를 보여줄래 편히
네 모습 그대로 그래 괜찮아 괜찮아도

두 손에 가득 채워질 추억들은
소중한 우리 이야기
진심이 담긴 마음이
시간이 지나 다시 기억할 수 있다면
말할 수 있을까
너도 행복했다고

너와 울고 같이 웃고
기대하고 아파했지
모든 걸 쏟고 사랑하고
마음이 가는 대로 있는 그대로

말하지 못할 고민거리
깊게 상처 난 자리
늘 같은 속도로 흘러가는 시간이
언제나 그랬듯이 씻어내줄 테니
흐르듯 살아도 그냥 괜찮아 괜찮아도

author: @inasazaliya7747
text:
Lirik dan terjemahan bahasa indonesia :

Suthage seuchyeogan gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Tekanan yang muncul karena terlalu banyak perasaan yang menumpuk

Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin maeumeul sumgineun beopdeul
Entah sejak kapan aku mulai terbiasa menyembunyikan perasaanku

Nan eodijjeume wa issna apman bogo dallyeoogiman haessdeon
Entah kemana sebenarnya tujuanku yang ku lakukan hanya terus berlari kedepan

Doraboneun geosdo waenji geobi na mirwodun yaegideul
Dengan perasaan takut untuk menoleh kebelakang kepada cerita kita yang tertunda

Sigani gadeut nae anen haengbokhaesseossdeon
Seiring waktu berjalan, aku merasa ada kebahagian dalam diriku

Ttaeron gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Terkadang aku juga merasa sedih

Maeil gati tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Aku menghabiskan waktuku seperti itu setiap hari

Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae
Seperti matahari dan bulan yang bergantian dengan alami

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Hari ini untuk pertama kalinya

Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Aku bertatapan dengan hatiku yang jujur

Geoul ape seoneun geosdo meomusdae
Aku berdiri didepan cermin

I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae
Namun entah mengapa, ekspresi lagi-lagi tampak canggung

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Hal-hal indah yang selalu berharga

Jamsi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Walaupun akan berlalu, setidaknya mereka pernah ada sedikit lebih lama

Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan ilsangeul chaeul maeumui nun
Hari-hariku selalu berjalan dengan normal

Geu ane gamchwodun oeroumdo jamsi meomul su issge hae
Biarkan rasa sepi itu hadir hanya untuk waktu yang singkat

Geujeo barabwa budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Perhatikanlah, jika angin lembut mulai berhembus menyelimuti

Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya
Saat itu adalah hari yang tepat untuk membuka hatimu

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Kenang-kenangan yang terkumul oleh kedua tangan kita

Sojunghan uri iyagi
Kisah kita yang berharga

Jinsimi damgin maeumi
Dan hati yang penuh ketulusan

Sigani jina dasi gieokhal su issdamyeon
Jika seiring waktu berjalan kamu masih mengingat semua itu

Malhal su isseulkka neodo haengbokhaessdago
Bolehkah aku mengira bahwa selama ini kamu juga merasa bahagia

Neowa ulgo gati usgo
Menangis dan tertawa bersama

Gidaehago apahaessji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Melupakan segalanya dan saling mencintai

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero

author: @ezgi8140
text: Do Kyungsoo ben bu gece de buradayım. Bana güvenebilir misin? Bu gece ile birlikte 4. gece olacak sanırım? Tam bilmiyorum ama yine senin sesinle uykuya dalacağım. Eşsiz sesin beni mest ediyor. Sesin yağmur sonrası gelen güzellikler gibi.. toprak kokusu, gökkuşağı, neşeli insanlar, açan güneş, sıcak gülümsemeler... sana bu kadar bağlanacağımı bilmiyordum. Eğer bir gün ayrılmak zorunda kalırsak, bunu isteyerek yaptığımı sakın düşünme meleğim olur mu? Seni çok seviyorum. Şimdi uyuyacağım saat 3 oldu burada. Senin için yeni bir gün başlıyor. Mutlu sabahlar bebeğim yarın gece yeniden burada olacağım♡♡

author: @winanuraeni4406
text:
Suthage seuchyeogan gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Tekanan yang muncul karena terlalu banyak perasaan yang menumpuk

Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin maeumeul sumgineun beopdeul
Entah sejak kapan aku mulai terbiasa menyembunyikan perasaanku

Nan eodijjeume wa issna apman bogo dallyeoogiman haessdeon
Entah kemana sebenarnya tujuanku yang ku lakukan hanya terus berlari kedepan

Doraboneun geosdo waenji geobi na mirwodun yaegideul
Dengan perasaan takut untuk menoleh kebelakang kepada cerita kita yang tertunda

Sigani gadeut nae anen haengbokhaesseossdeon
Seiring waktu berjalan, aku merasa ada kebahagian dalam diriku

Ttaeron gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Terkadang aku juga merasa sedih

Maeil gati tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Aku menghabiskan waktuku seperti itu setiap hari

Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae
Seperti matahari dan bulan yang bergantian dengan alami

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Hari ini untuk pertama kalinya

Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Aku bertatapan dengan hatiku yang jujur

Geoul ape seoneun geosdo meomusdae
Aku berdiri didepan cermin

I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae
Namun entah mengapa, ekspresi lagi-lagi tampak canggung

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Hal-hal indah yang selalu berharga

Jamsi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Walaupun akan berlalu, setidaknya mereka pernah ada sedikit lebih lama

Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan ilsangeul chaeul maeumui nun
Hari-hariku selalu berjalan dengan normal

Geu ane gamchwodun oeroumdo jamsi meomul su issge hae
Biarkan rasa sepi itu hadir hanya untuk waktu yang singkat

Geujeo barabwa budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Perhatikanlah, jika angin lembut mulai berhembus menyelimuti

Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya
Saat itu adalah hari yang tepat untuk membuka hatimu

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Kenang-kenangan yang terkumul oleh kedua tangan kita

Sojunghan uri iyagi
Kisah kita yang berharga

Jinsimi damgin maeumi
Dan hati yang penuh ketulusan

Sigani jina dasi gieokhal su issdamyeon
Jika seiring waktu berjalan kamu masih mengingat semua itu

Malhal su isseulkka neodo haengbokhaessdago
Bolehkah aku mengira bahwa selama ini kamu juga merasa bahagia

Neowa ulgo gati usgo
Menangis dan tertawa bersama

Gidaehago apahaessji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Melupakan segalanya dan saling mencintai

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama seperti yang hati kita rasakan

Malhaji moshal gomingeori
Sebuah kegelisahan yang tidak bisa diutarakan

Gipge sangcheo nan jari
Sebuah luka yang dalam

Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun sigani
Waktu akan selalu berjalan dengan kecepatan yang sama

Eonjena geuraessdeusi ssiseonaejul teni
Suatu saat nanti, aku akan menghapus semua lukamu

Heureudeut sarado geunyang gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kita hidup hanya dengan mengikuti alur yang berjalan, itu tidak apa-apa
